WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
I am not leaving without you.

2
00:00:04.219 --> 00:00:06.940
You're trying to escape? Never!

3
00:00:06.940 --> 00:00:11.939
But now, we fight?

4
00:00:11.939 --> 00:00:13.460
Go now, I'll hold her off.

5
00:00:13.460 --> 00:00:14.740
Go! Please!

6
00:00:14.740 --> 00:00:15.779
Nobody is running!

7
00:00:17.539 --> 00:00:19.699
I called you here to discuss the sacrifice.

8
00:00:20.929 --> 00:00:22.370
What is there to discuss?

9
00:00:23.010 --> 00:00:26.850
As the heir you have forfeited the sacrificial offering,

10
00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:30.289
it is imperative that you recover her.

11
00:00:30.929 --> 00:00:35.020
To continue, she is the chosen witch.

12
00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:38.060
It would be a waste to kill her off now.

13
00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:39.979
I do not want to kill her.

14
00:00:40.619 --> 00:00:43.420
Marrying her as queen won't affect the ritual.

15
00:00:43.420 --> 00:00:49.520
Have you forgotten how your mother died?

16
00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.600
Damn it, I can't take them on by myself.

17
00:00:58.579 --> 00:01:00.820
Who's there? Show yourself!

